Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呦！阿虛　你在這裡幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不出來嗎　當搬運工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈　還真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定又是涼宮的命令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來半年過去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.70,0:15:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同班同學也已經十分了解我的處境了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還要回去學校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.60,0:15:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掰啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.25,0:15:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去　開始下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣預報明明說降雨機率只有１０％
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一點也不準的氣象預報
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.00,0:15:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望不會轉成大雨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:15:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎啊　下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛不會有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在並不留戀著那間房間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想快點喝到朝比奈學姊泡的茶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫暖我的身體和心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀吼　實玖瑠在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦　只有長門在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要找她跟我交換明天的掃除值日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.55,0:16:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這我才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實玖瑠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.70,0:16:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔喔　在那裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.30,0:17:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦　阿虛你剛才出門辦事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴屋學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.05,0:17:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟她說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼　辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　你淋濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見啦　手帕等等跟這個一起交給實玖瑠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還是老樣子　讓人看不出下個舉動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是個通情達理的前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.75,0:17:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦　長門
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有妳在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日他們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:18:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對　就是要一屁股坐在跳箱上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來妳已經開竅了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來就像是一個恍神的笨拙女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳該不會是故意做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古泉　拿一下這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.35,0:18:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個要這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那三個人現在在哪做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然有點在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在搬運大型行李上坡的疲勞就已經夠我受的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且想到相同的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等回家時還要再走一次　就更覺得累了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.95,0:18:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手好冰冷喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.60,0:20:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　只有妳在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊　不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.90,0:20:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.15,0:20:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒在我臉上塗鴉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.85,0:20:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會做這麼幼稚的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外三個人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你睡的很沉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只剩妳還留在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫不醒　社辦又必須上鎖了才能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.35,0:20:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且現在也還在下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.70,0:21:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.50,0:21:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羊毛衫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中一件無疑是春日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.15,0:21:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過　那另一件是誰的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.20,0:21:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說朝比奈學姐在我睡著時換了衣服了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.40,0:21:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.60,0:21:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要真的睡著       
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.45,0:21:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是裝睡的話‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.15,0:21:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了　差不多是離校的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.39,0:21:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　可是真糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.70,0:21:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒有帶傘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.60,0:21:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一把傘就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.60,0:21:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再靠過來一點啦　我都淋濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.30,0:21:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經靠的很過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.60,0:21:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　這把傘不是妳的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.90,0:22:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面寫著「職員用」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.25,0:22:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是學校的備用品
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.10,0:22:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給學生用也不是什麼壞事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說　你想要淋溼掉回去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.70,0:22:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不借你撐囉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.22,0:22:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.50,0:22:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧我還幫妳搬暖爐回來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.30,0:22:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連一句慰勞的話都不會說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.20,0:22:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這個團長大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.30,0:22:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.40,0:23:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回　涼宮春日的憂鬱　第四話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.95,0:23:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.70,0:23:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回　涼宮春日的憂鬱　第十話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.00,0:23:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼宮春日的憂鬱　四
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.85,0:23:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道各位還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.10,0:23:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門的那個令我迷惑的驚人告白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.30,0:23:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放棄儘管跟來吧